s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"你覺得而家報警有用？"},{"pid":"5f6bc3d373355305834f4cdb64c2b4ee68ec402e","tid":1443492,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"日日 CALL 食環去北角富臨"},{"pid":"e93945a37dcaaac213bd104834d4b6d2814cedc0","tid":1443492,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"如果建立一個頁面，將有質素既討論同行動post分類，並且定期更新，有無得諗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442327/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442327/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgAHYfb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgAHYfb.png&h=f12991ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>戰術討論</strong> <br />\n行動方向<br />\n見到街坊影相要講「多謝支持」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1443046/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1443046/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n再搞街坊即割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442224/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442224/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[煽動內鬥］國泰單野就係要你地香港人自相殘殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438147/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438147/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n共 產 黨 嘅 行 動 方 向 其 實 已 經 好 明 顯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1440370/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1440370/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向<br />\n【唔該做返主動】我地渣住幾多核彈係手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1435712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1435712/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n仔女比TVB更入屋 停止同父母割裂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441145/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441145/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非：打破防火牆，用區塊鏈把文宣及資訊倒流中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1435137/pa